# Build artifacts that may appear if e2e fixtures are smoke-tested natively.
# The fixtures themselves are checked in; everything generated must stay out.
**/target/
**/build/
**/Cargo.lock
**/shard.lock
**/lib/**/*.so
**/lib/**/*.dylib
**/.bundle/
**/vendor/
**/node_modules/
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
**/.omnipackage/
**/.env
